name: Pluto
description:
The first of its kind, $PLUTO ties a narrative to universal basic income (UBI) driven by the
community that collaborates on a “choose-your-own-adventure” model of governance to propel
Pepe across the galaxy and earn $PLUTO and PlutoPepe Tokens ($PEPE) in return. Vote on major
network decisions disguised as plot points on Pepe’s adventure to improve the network in a
decentralized fashion.
